Meta Tag - Specify Instructions for a Field - cml:instructions

- Used to specify the instructions for a form element
- Can only be the child tag of a form element
- If used in conjunction with an [code]instructions[/code] attribute in the parent form element, only the value of the [code]instructions[/code] attribute will be used

[code]
<cml:radios label="Sample radio buttons:"> 
<cml:instructions>Check one of these.</cml:instructions> 
<cml:radio label="Radio 1" /> 
<cml:radio label="Radio 2" /> 
<cml:radio label="Radio 3" /> 
</cml:radios>
[/code]

